23
00:02:41,079 --> 00:02:41,840
No.

24
00:02:43,110 --> 00:02:50,060
[Yang Kaizhi, Revolutionary]

25
00:02:43,270 --> 00:02:46,680
Currently, the Empress Dowager and the Emperor have gone to survey Xi'an.

26
