00:35:02,330 --> 00:35:05,400
Don't you want to go to Shanghai?

569
00:35:14,690 --> 00:35:22,770
[Shanghai]

570
00:35:27,230 --> 00:35:32,920
[On the 5th month of the 27th year of Guangxu (July 1901), under the diplomatic coercion and military threats of imperialism,]

571
00:35:32,950 --> 00:35:39,840
[The Qing government sent Emperor Guangxu's younger brother, Aisin Gioro Zaifeng, to Germany from Beijing to submit an apology letter.]

572
00:36:09,890 --> 00:36:12,620
The Eight-Nation Alliance has occupied Beijing

573
00:36:12,760 --> 00:36:14,400
and the North is at war.

574
00:36:15,510 --> 00:36:19,590
We alone can enjoy prosperity.

575
00:36:16,140 --> 00:36:19,180
[Shanghai Qinghe Qinlou Villa]

576
00:36:21,230 --> 00:36:22,590
Prince Chun

577
00:36:21,660 --> 00:36:24,880
[Vice President of Shanghai Business Association, Song Baoquan]

578
00:36:22,590 --> 00:36:23,840
is visiting Germany.

579
00:36:24,110 --> 00:36:25,320
He will pass by here

580
00:36:26,070 --> 00:36:27,400
and board the ship here.

581
00:36:27,600 --> 00:36:28,800
This is the time

582
00:36:28,830 --> 00:36:31,190
to show our loyalty.

583
00:36:31,550 --> 00:36:33,110
We should be respectful

584
00:36:33,150 --> 00:36:35,840
and welcome them with all our hearts.

585
00:36:36,000 --> 00:36:36,760
Right?

586
00:36:36,880 --> 00:36:37,840
Yes!

587
00:36:46,640 --> 00:36:47,680
Mr. Song.

588
00:36:49,000 --> 00:36:51,400
This is the latest car model of 1900.

589
00:36:51,800 --> 00:36:53,930
There is only one such car in Shanghai.

590
00:36:54,110 --> 00:36:56,710
It was transported from London three days ago.

591
00:36:56,900 --> 00:36:58,230
It's very fashionable.

592
00:37:00,370 --> 00:37:02,440
Charlie, drive it away.

593
00:37:02,880 --> 00:37:04,070
My lifestyle

594
00:37:04,070 --> 00:37:05,200
is not so luxurious.

595
00:37:05,960 --> 00:37:07,590
Drive this to the Chamber of Foreign Affairs.

596
00:37:07,590 --> 00:37:09,850
Have it ready for Prince Chun's use only.

597
00:37:52,150 --> 00:37:53,070
Who are you?

598
00:38:02,620 --> 00:38:04,480
These are the independent army wealth coupons

599
00:38:04,480 --> 00:38:05,960
you bought last year.

600
00:38:06,260 --> 00:38:07,790
I brought them here for you.

601
00:38:08,440 --> 00:38:09,900
It's 20,000 yuan in total.

602
00:38:10,320 --> 00:38:11,380
Please have a look.

603
00:38:11,590 --> 00:38:13,250
You worked for Tang Caichang.

604
00:38:24,630 --> 00:38:26,030
Boping was my brother.

605
00:38:27,590 --> 00:38:28,960
Last year, I did buy

606
00:38:28,960 --> 00:38:31,490
20,000 yuan worth of his army wealth coupons.

607
00:38:32,320 --> 00:38:34,960
But the right of the past is wrong in the present.

608
00:38:34,960 --> 00:38:37,000
What a pity, young man.

609
00:38:37,550 --> 00:38:40,230
Zhang Zhidong mercilessly killed the revolutionaries

610
00:38:40,230 --> 00:38:41,960
and beheaded my brother.

611
00:38:42,320 --> 00:38:43,760
Do you think I would still invest

612
00:38:43,760 --> 00:38:45,290
in this pile of waste paper?

613
00:38:45,710 --> 00:38:47,970
But the Commander-in-chief told me that

614
00:38:48,150 --> 00:38:50,350
no matter the result of the revolution,

615
00:38:50,400 --> 00:38:51,840
I must hand these coupons

616
00:38:52,110 --> 00:38:54,030
to you personally.

617
00:38:54,960 --> 00:38:56,080
As people,

618
00:38:56,510 --> 00:38:58,020
we should keep our promises.

619
00:38:58,020 --> 00:38:59,020
What do you think?

620
00:39:03,550 --> 00:39:05,680
I won't make things difficult for you.

621
00:39:06,000 --> 00:39:06,860
Chairman Song,

622
00:39:07,510 --> 00:39:09,240
you can deal with these coupons

623
00:39:09,400 --> 00:39:10,400
however you want.

624
00:39:11,000 --> 00:39:11,800
But...

625
00:39:13,320 --> 00:39:14,710
Can you do me a favor?

626
00:39:17,690 --> 00:39:18,480
Go ahead.

627
00:39:19,230 --> 00:39:20,320
I heard that

628
00:39:20,400 --> 00:39:23,230
you just sponsored the Viceroy of Liangjiang

629
00:39:23,510 --> 00:39:25,970
to send military students to study in Japan.

630
00:39:26,400 --> 00:39:27,400
Yes, I did.

631
00:39:29,510 --> 00:39:30,550
Then...

632
00:39:32,320 --> 00:39:33,850
Can I be one of the students?

633
00:39:46,400 --> 00:39:47,120
Hello.

634
00:39:47,290 --> 00:39:49,000
Is Yang Yifan here?

635
00:39:48,100 --> 00:39:53,390
[Shanghai Girls' School]

636
00:39:50,030 --> 00:39:52,320
Mr. Yang. Mr. Yang.

637
00:39:53,070 --> 00:39:54,360
Finding you was difficult.

638
00:39:54,360 --> 00:39:55,070
I heard that

639
00:39:55,280 --> 00:39:56,880
the emperor's younger brother is in Shanghai.

640
00:39:56,880 --> 00:39:57,800
The main road was

641
00:39:57,800 --> 00:39:58,960
completely jam-packed.

642
00:39:58,960 --> 00:40:00,510
It was quite a grand setup.

643
00:40:00,710 --> 00:40:01,320
Brother-in-law.

644
00:40:01,320 --> 00:40:03,550
Why is His Majesty's brother making a scene?

645
00:40:03,550 --> 00:40:05,080
It's nothing to be proud of.

646
00:40:05,150 --> 00:40:06,030
It's shameful.

647
00:40:06,070 --> 00:40:07,800
Shameful? Why?

648
00:40:07,880 --> 00:40:09,210
They failed to win the battle.

649
00:40:09,210 --> 00:40:09,810
Careful.

650
00:40:10,510 --> 00:40:12,190
They couldn't sign the peace agreement in Beijing either.

651
00:40:12,190 --> 00:40:14,070
So, the Eight-Nation Alliance stated that

652
00:40:14,070 --> 00:40:15,710
the imperial court must send a first-tier prince

653
00:40:15,710 --> 00:40:16,360
to Germany

654
00:40:16,360 --> 00:40:17,630
and submit a letter of apology.

655
00:40:17,630 --> 00:40:19,110
Isn't it shameful?

656
00:40:19,970 --> 00:40:20,810
Hanhua.

657
00:40:20,840 --> 00:40:22,510
You managed to recruit a student?

658
00:40:22,510 --> 00:40:23,150
Not at all.

659
00:40:23,450 --> 00:40:24,910
This is my sister-in-law.

660
00:40:25,800 --> 00:40:27,360
We've been in the newspaper for seven days.

661
00:40:27,360 --> 00:40:28,800
We haven't got a single student.

662
00:40:28,800 --> 00:40:30,860
We'll take our time, there's no rush.

663
00:40:31,150 --> 00:40:32,070
I was wondering why they were

664
00:40:32,070 --> 00:40:33,070
so excited to see me.

665
00:40:33,070 --> 00:40:33,590
Another day,

666
00:40:33,590 --> 00:40:35,070
another sum of rent to pay.

667
00:40:35,230 --> 00:40:36,550
Who organized this school?

668
00:40:36,550 --> 00:40:37,320
I did.

669
00:40:37,340 --> 00:40:41,990
[Principal of Shanghai Girls' School, Yang Yifan]
[Courtesy name: Hanhua]

670
00:40:37,690 --> 00:40:38,290
You did?

671
00:40:38,360 --> 00:40:39,360
Surprising, isn't it?

672
00:40:39,360 --> 00:40:41,400
That's how things are in the Settlement.

673
00:40:41,400 --> 00:40:42,960
You can do any business

674
00:40:42,960 --> 00:40:43,840
and anything.

675
00:40:43,960 --> 00:40:45,030
On your own,

676
00:40:45,030 --> 00:40:46,230
you can own a big bank,

677
00:40:46,280 --> 00:40:47,800
a big store, a big factory,

678
00:40:47,880 --> 00:40:49,070
and even a school.

679
00:40:49,320 --> 00:40:50,070
No one will stop you.

680
00:40:50,070 --> 00:40:51,870
You can teach whatever you want.

681
00:40:52,110 --> 00:40:54,360
There's only one type of rent tax called the Police Patrol Contribution.

682
00:40:54,360 --> 00:40:55,960
The rest is up to you,

683
00:40:56,110 --> 00:40:57,630
be it the school's rules

684
00:40:57,800 --> 00:40:58,860
or the curriculum.

685
00:40:59,480 --> 00:41:01,480
But why do you want to start a school?

686
00:41:02,550 --> 00:41:03,410
Good question.

687
00:41:06,710 --> 00:41:07,800
The cost is so high.

688
00:41:08,000 --> 00:41:09,660
Can you make money out of this?

689
00:41:09,800 --> 00:41:12,030
My sister would be worried if she knew.

690
00:41:12,550 --> 00:41:15,150
You are more like your father than your sister.

691
00:41:15,550 --> 00:41:16,800
All right, you can stay here.

692
00:41:16,800 --> 00:41:17,860
It's empty anyway.

693
00:41:17,880 --> 00:41:19,070
I need to discuss things

694
00:41:19,070 --> 00:41:20,000
with my colleagues.

695
00:41:20,000 --> 00:41:21,880
There are so many troublesome things to handle.

696
00:41:21,880 --> 00:41:23,070
Wait, Brother-in-law.

697
00:41:23,070 --> 00:41:24,280
Why didn't you take a look?

698
00:41:24,280 --> 00:41:25,030
My sister brought you a bunch of

699
00:41:25,030 --> 00:41:26,180
food and necessities.

700
00:41:26,180 --> 00:41:27,640
We'll talk about it later.

701
00:41:27,850 --> 00:41:28,560
By the way,

702
00:41:28,760 --> 00:41:30,290
before you leave Shanghai,

703
00:41:30,300 --> 00:41:31,500
I'll show you around,

704
00:41:31,520 --> 00:41:32,360
okay?

705
00:41:32,420 --> 00:41:33,800
No rush, Brother-in-law.

706
00:41:33,800 --> 00:41:35,510
Can't we take our time?

707
00:41:35,800 --> 00:41:37,330
I can even stay and help you.

708
00:41:37,510 --> 00:41:38,550
Help me?

709
00:41:40,030 --> 00:41:40,880
How?

710
00:41:41,230 --> 00:41:42,560
I can't be a teacher.

711
00:41:42,760 --> 00:41:44,340
But I can be a student, right?

712
00:41:44,340 --> 00:41:45,020
All deals

713
00:41:45,040 --> 00:41:45,880
are the same.

714
00:41:45,910 --> 00:41:47,200
You have to first make yourself known.

715
00:41:47,200 --> 00:41:48,230
We've been doing that.

716
00:41:48,230 --> 00:41:49,840
We have been advertising our place for a week now.

717
00:41:49,840 --> 00:41:51,570
You can start your class first.

718
00:41:51,590 --> 00:41:53,030
If there are no students,

719
00:41:54,230 --> 00:41:55,960
invite all the ladies and maids here.

720
00:41:55,960 --> 00:41:56,760
The more,

721
00:41:56,850 --> 00:41:57,600
the merrier.

722
00:41:57,620 --> 00:41:59,070
They'll be your temporary students.

723
00:41:59,070 --> 00:42:01,800
Once you start offering classes, you'll gain popularity.

724
00:42:01,800 --> 00:42:03,110
Then, you can build a reputation

725
00:42:03,110 --> 00:42:04,480
and attract actual students.

726
00:42:04,480 --> 00:42:05,550
Good idea.

727
00:42:06,320 --> 00:42:07,550
You're just like your father,

728
00:42:07,550 --> 00:42:09,210
so much more than your sister.

729
00:42:48,280 --> 00:42:50,210
[Shenghe Hotel]

730
00:42:50,310 --> 00:42:52,580
[Reception for military students in Japan]
